title: 3 Bedroom Pent House Coming soon! Must See!
posting_body: ['Welcome Home to The Highland!', 'CALL:', 'show contact info', 'x473', '$7,172', '.', '3 Bed 3 Bath .', '1391 Sq.Ft', '* Unit 623 - Available 09/08/22', 'The Highland', 'Address:', '1411 North Highland Avenue Hollywood, CA 90028', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Enjoy a luxury lifestyle when you lease this three-bedroom, three-bathroom apartment at The Highland Residences.', 'With Dream Suite, you can control the shades, room temperature, and lights from your smartphone.', 'In the designer kitchen, you will have modern cabinets, a full backsplash, and stainless steel appliances.', 'The quartz countertops in both the kitchen and bathrooms add a touch of elegance.', 'With the inclusion of a full-size washer and dryer, you can do your laundry from the comfort of home.', 'This pet-friendly community has a rooftop deck where residents can take advantage of the pool area or the fitness center.', 'Residents are free to walk their pets in the pet park or use the grilling areas for barbecue cookouts.', 'The community also has an outdoor fireplace and a co-working space.', 'Schedule a private tour today!', 'OFFICE\u2002 \u2002HOURS', 'Tuesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Wednesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Thursday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Friday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Saturday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'CALL US TODAY!', 'show contact info', 'x473', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
